#id=1
#text=I had just finished eating my lunch and knew it was time to go grocery shopping for the week .
#id=2
#text=I always buy my groceries all at one time for the week and then cook everything over the weekend so that I do n't have to cook on a daily basis .
#id=3
#text=Anyway , I hopped in my car and drove to Walmart which is where I usually do all my grocery shopping .
#id=4
#text=I found a parking space close to the entrance because I knew I was going to buy a lot .
#id=5
#text=I got out of the car , walked through the store doors , and grabbed a shopping cart along the way .
#id=6
#text=I made my way down the fruit and vegetable aisles first , picking up bananas , oranges , salad mix , and kale along the way .
#id=7
#text=I then added some fish , chicken , hamburger meat , and pork to my cart .
#id=8
#text=Moving along down the aisles , I picked up all the dairy goods , spices , and snacks I would need for the week .
#id=9
#text=With my cart stacked high , I headed to the check out line where the cashier greeted me warmly and began ringing my items up .
#text=My total came to $ 101.43 which was a lot of money but definitely worth it .
#text=The cashier bagged my groceries as I paid .
#text=Then , I pushed my cart full of groceries out of the store and to the parking lot where I would load them into my trunk .
#text=I put the cart in the cart holding area and drove away .
